🎯 Why Do We Use Packages?
✔ 1. Avoid Name Conflicts
Two classes with same name can exist in different packages.

✔ 2. Better Code Organization
Makes large projects easier to manage.

✔ 3. Access Protection
public, protected, default accessibility depends on packages.

✔ 4. Reusability
Package classes can be reused across projects.

